{
  "stem": "21731.2",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And also the firm in Lwow where my husband had his silk shirts-- white silk shirts with the monogram 'MS' written.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "They were from a firm, [?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Stark, ?] and they were Jewish.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And also, there was a firm with [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] writing paper, and, and pens, and what do you call-- stationary.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "But they had also very beautiful leather things that was the name of [?",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Probst. ?] They were Jewish.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "So-- but that was in Lwow.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So coming back to Warsaw, I saw quite a lot.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I was very impressed by everything.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Oh, yes, and I had my pearls knotted because they were not knotted, which-- when I took them to the jeweler to have them, I think, valued for an insurance or something.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I don't know why they were taken, why my husband took me to this jeweller.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And the jeweller saw they are not knotted.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "He could not understand pearls of this value not knotted, because if you-- if it breaks, you lose all.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And if you break a knotted, [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] knotted-- [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] you call it?",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Pearl.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "You just lose one.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Then you lose only one.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Anyway, they were-- they were counted.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "He signed that there were 129.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So I remember this.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So it must have made a great impression on me if I remember today-- 129 pearls.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And the next day, we came to fetch them.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Naturally, they are much longer now because they were knotted.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So then we left for Cracow.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We-- I forgot the name of the hotel.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It was certainly a very good hotel.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And there I went the first time in my life in a sled, which was [PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS] with two horses.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "What do you call it?",
      "word_count": 5
    }
  ],
